    </li>
    <li id="fn:2">
      <p><code>sass/custom/_print.scss</code> at commit <a href="https://github.com/VincentTam/vincenttam.github.io/commit/4be1bbf">4be1bbf</a> <a href="#fnref:2" class="reversefootnote">&#8617;</a></p>
